videos.headline: Colorado State WR cuts deficit in half with leaping grab
videos.description: Colorado State QB K.J. Carta-Samuels connects with WR Olabisi Johnson on a 26-yard TD to cut deficit in half.

videos.headline: Colorado WR pins ball to face mask for TD catch
videos.description: Colorado WR Juwann Winfree pulls in TD catch to take a 28-7 lead.

videos.headline: Colorado RB side steps defenders for explosive 49-yard TD
videos.description: Colorado RB Travon McMillian side steps a couple defenders for a 49-yard TD, pushing the lead to 42-10.
